{"tid":2258570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Youtube內講拜登醜聞即「黃標」甚至將影片18禁","createTime":"2020-10-26T06:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T11:24:59.000Z","uid":19552,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5042195b5e47a4e8bbb9000d8770b4435d3d296d","tid":2258570,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"美國總統大選將在下月3日舉行，總統候選人之一的拜登與兒子杭特被爆出「電郵門」風波，但相關新聞卻被社群平台限制張貼。如今，「年代向錢看」粉專質疑YouTube也是如此，十分火大。<br />\n<br />\n拜登與杭特爆出電郵門事件，但相關新聞在推特、臉書限制張貼。然而，「年代向錢看」粉專PO出節目上談論拜登卻被YouTube黃標的圖片，不滿地說：「幹！YouTube好維護拜登啊！幹！又賞我們黃標一枚！」並諷刺「偽善的平台跟媒體真多」。<br />\n<br />\n其中，影片一旦被標示為黃標，即該影片無法透過廣告進行盈利，只是為何被判定為黃標，創作者也無從分辨。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLO93bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLO93bc.png&h=dc42b54b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"216af35e4fe2e8c9e1db19e1700cb2d9b7ee2b3a","tid":2258570,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be52f044a60afa0e482bf6995136c952f9cfa1cc","tid":2258570,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:56:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1afe59b9c3fa8d9534df2dab5c3c5fb3baa3db15","tid":2258570,"uid":20867,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T07:01:52.000Z","msg":"英語世界就話可以censor「Biden」「childporn」呢D keywords<br />\n<br />\n華語世界都censor到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9df0e6c9d741155881a4e799d7dbc18ec096a3","tid":2258570,"uid":19552,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"1afe59b9c3fa8d9534df2dab5c3c5fb3baa3db15","tid":2258570,"uid":20867,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T07:01:52.000Z","msg":"英語世界就話可以censor「Biden」「childporn」呢D keywords<br />\n<br />\n華語世界都censor到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-2